Package com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types

Defines package version.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Account
    Defines an interface about an Account available with the email provider for a particular client.
    BaseType
    This is the base type for all entities defined for email provider interface.
    ConnectionParams
    This interface manages the connection parameters for an email provider.
    Email
    Defines interface of email/newsletter to be sent to emailprovider.
    EmailTools
    Defines interface for all the tools that are supported by external mail provider.
    ListAttribute  
    NamedType
    Defines interface of a BaseType that also has a name.
    PersonalizationInfo
    Defines interface for all the Personalization mappings for an email provider.
    SendClassification
    Defines interface for all Send classifications that are available that can be used to send an email through the email provider.
    Subscriber
    Defines interface for subscriber(lead) to the external email provider.
    SubscriptionList
    Defines interface for a subscription list on the external email provider.
